Police in Migwani, Kitui County are investigating a case where a woman reportedly stole Sh8,000 from a man she had an affair with.An unnamed police officer at the station said the man reported the matter and the woman was arrested. PHOTO: COURTESYAn unnamed police officer at the station said the man reported the matter and the woman was arrested.However, she was freed after police discovered she may have suffered injuries in her private parts. The woman claimed the man inflicted the injuries on her when she was asleep. The woman admitted to the police of stealing Sh4,000 and not Sh8,000 from the man as he claimed.Witnesses say the man met the woman, who is known to him, in Migwani town and the two were taking alcohol at a local bar.The woman was advised to seek medical help as investigations start. - Paul Mutua